---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Beacon • CV'nin Gerçek Potansiyelini Keşfet">
<!-- 1. NAVBAR (Fixed) -->
<nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 bg-surface border-b border-outline-variant transition-all duration-200">
<div class="flex justify-between items-center h-[72px] px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop max-w-max-width mx-auto">
<a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3">
  <img src="/mixboard-image.png" alt="Beacon Logo" class="h-9 w-auto object-contain" />
  <span class="font-headline-md text-headline-md font-bold text-on-surface">Beacon</span>
</a>
<div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8">
<a class="font-body-sm text-body-sm font-semibold text-primary border-b-2 border-primary pb-1 transition-colors duration-200" href="/login">Özellikler</a>
<a class="font-body-sm text-body-sm font-semibold text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-200" href="/login">Nasıl Çalışır</a>
<a class="font-body-sm text-body-sm font-semibold text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-200" href="/login">SSS</a>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
<a href="/login" class="hidden md:block font-body-sm text-body-sm font-semibold text-on-surface hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-200">Giriş Yap</a>
<a href="/register" class="bg-primary-container text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-display text-body-sm font-semibold hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">Başla</a>
</div>
</div>
</nav>
<!-- 2. HERO -->
<section class="pt-32 pb-24 px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop max-w-max-width mx-auto text-center flex flex-col items-center">
<span class="font-label-md text-label-md text-primary-container tracking-wider uppercase mb-6 inline-block bg-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-outline-variant">AI DESTEKLİ CV ANALİZİ</span>
<h1 class="font-display text-display text-on-surface mb-6 max-w-3xl leading-tight">CV'nin gerçek potansiyelini keşfet.</h1>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">CV'ni yükle, yapay zeka güçlü yönlerini, zayıf yönlerini ve gelişim önerilerini saniyeler içinde analiz etsin.</p>
<a href="/register" class="bg-primary-container text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-display text-body-md font-semibold hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity mb-8 h-[52px] flex items-center justify-center">Ücretsiz Analiz Et</a>
<div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 md:gap-8 mb-16">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-outline-variant shadow-sm">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container text-sm">check</span>
<span class="font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface">Ücretsiz</span>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-outline-variant shadow-sm">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-sm">bolt</span>
<span class="font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface">Saniyeler içinde</span>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-outline-variant shadow-sm">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container text-sm">lock</span>
<span class="font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface">Güvenli</span>
</div>
</div>

</section>
<!-- 3. PROBLEM SECTION -->
<section class="bg-surface-container-lowest py-24 px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
<div class="max-w-max-width mx-auto">
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-on-surface mb-12 text-center">CV'n yeterince iyi mi?</h2>
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
<div class="bg-surface p-8 rounded-xl border-l-[3px] border-primary-container shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-on-surface mb-4">01 Görünmez kalan yetenekler</h3>
<p class="font-body-sm text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">Standart şablonlar, gerçek potansiyelinizi ve benzersiz becerilerinizi yeterince öne çıkaramayabilir.</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-surface p-8 rounded-xl border-l-[3px] border-primary-container shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-on-surface mb-4">02 İşe alımcılar ne istiyor?</h3>
<p class="font-body-sm text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">Sektör trendleri hızla değişiyor. CV'niz güncel gereksinimleri ve anahtar kelimeleri karşılıyor mu?</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-surface p-8 rounded-xl border-l-[3px] border-primary-container shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-on-surface mb-4">03 Geri bildirim yok</h3>
<p class="font-body-sm text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">Başvurularınızdan neden yanıt alamadığınızı anlamak için objektif ve anında bir değerlendirmeye ihtiyacınız var.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- 4. SOLUTION SECTION -->
<section class="py-24 px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop bg-surface">
<div class="max-w-max-width mx-auto">
<div class="text-center mb-16">
<span class="font-label-md text-label-md text-primary-container tracking-wider uppercase mb-4 inline-block">ÇÖZÜM</span>
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-on-surface">Beacon CV'ni anlayan bir asistan.</h2>
</div>
<div class="space-y-24">
<!-- Block 1 -->
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
<div class="flex-1 md:pr-12">
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface mb-4">Anında Analiz</h3>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Yapay zeka motorumuz CV'nizi saniyeler içinde tarar ve derinlemesine bir analiz raporu sunar. Beklemek yok, anında sonuç.</p>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 w-full">
<img alt="Anında Analiz" class="w-full aspect-video md:aspect-[4/3] object-cover rounded-xl shadow-md border border-outline-variant" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida/AP1WRLs4-LeZi60cjZhN6_3aqfifupcVu1rvdez586xxayLcosjhdYahD08yxwcfAMw3iS2MrZkoi9xXofav0Uy2Fsvn4ato7_SFi0iJ2BZknDo8YfzYm0Bz7Guc0HG5UDPGQJqO8mEIPS5SSoN3oFye7j9nMUdc6Fq6lyDBiuXxWtqdK5kLC_JS-_GTYbFcqGjo09-4KwsL55JIWum0xJzrFkeWxTyZoTEj6D0P_XKDLcqbwSsxgEFwYty3esu0">
</div>
</div>
<!-- Block 2 -->
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-12">
<div class="flex-1 md:pl-12">
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface mb-4">Güçlü ve Zayıf Yönler</h3>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Hangi konularda öne çıktığınızı ve hangi alanlarda eksik olduğunuzu net bir şekilde görün. Rakiplerinizin bir adım önüne geçin.</p>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 w-full">
<img alt="Güçlü ve Zayıf Yönler" class="w-full aspect-video md:aspect-[4/3] object-cover rounded-xl shadow-md border border-outline-variant" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida/AP1WRLsspW7GAYdA-trt9gOFAxKVm8pYHyu65M8cEDZ_-8tRebKrQEvyqijx-peo6GFdOwO6FKII5sr9sUvsD6hYq76Vbbke_9tsd1AxWKzpqedvjMeW9p_K1MPYbbJTEeezA9ExDYJ9a05QlEUuag39soleGpxn9RCMg-pLiH5Q_tMMKga3uLe81-fjPSfIzMp30_A_0kvGmWRmkv5UWdHWH21oXOb2pAA_WUbkOL9vtml8IeGDIVSv4cqz7gzb">
</div>
</div>
<!-- Block 3 -->
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
<div class="flex-1 md:pr-12">
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface mb-4">Kişisel Gelişim Önerileri</h3>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Sadece eleştirmez, yol gösteririz. Eksik yönlerinizi nasıl geliştirebileceğinize dair kişiselleştirilmiş, eyleme geçirilebilir tavsiyeler alın.</p>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 w-full">
<img alt="Kişisel Gelişim Önerileri" class="w-full aspect-video md:aspect-[4/3] object-cover rounded-xl shadow-md border border-outline-variant" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida/AP1WRLvyJDWF0_vI8dpL9WO4jA7xMqIkhRB_NF121WEKlqxxFmUtJgqzNAoVw2WJNPJRVHae5q65-IKR0kOLpHYQcGvtLIuD5JxhX3IF-n57RZceg6epEF_ePotbapO6lJmoyNjMK9BqvBa7j-uY1y-lBEeTzBI63kUXbsmcF_4TGzlzhTRz7vPcdW8Ycdd7CCcTa9eZdKvyfRJVgbnhQ9MvrwzUAKY5y_8B4al8FxVI6ef5AzZPB1RCDc8GaMX3">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- 5. HOW IT WORKS -->
<section class="bg-surface-container-lowest py-24 px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="max-w-max-width mx-auto relative z-10">
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-on-surface mb-16 text-center">3 adımda CV analizin hazır.</h2>
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center relative">
<!-- Connecting Line for Desktop -->

<div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center w-full md:w-1/3 mb-12 md:mb-0 bg-surface-container-lowest p-4">
<div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary-container text-white flex items-center justify-center font-headline-md text-headline-md mb-6 shadow-md z-10">1</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-on-surface mb-2">CV'ni Yükle</h3>
<p class="font-body-sm text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">PDF veya Word formatındaki özgeçmişinizi sisteme yükleyin.</p>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center w-full md:w-1/3 mb-12 md:mb-0 bg-surface-container-lowest p-4">
<div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary-container text-white flex items-center justify-center font-headline-md text-headline-md mb-6 shadow-md z-10">2</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-on-surface mb-2">AI Analiz Etsin</h3>
<p class="font-body-sm text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">Gelişmiş algoritmalarımız saniyeler içinde verilerinizi işler.</p>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center w-full md:w-1/3 bg-surface-container-lowest p-4">
<div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary-container text-white flex items-center justify-center font-headline-md text-headline-md mb-6 shadow-md z-10">3</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-on-surface mb-2">Sonuçları Gör</h3>
<p class="font-body-sm text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">Detaylı raporunuzu inceleyin ve hemen aksiyon alın.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- 6. FEATURES -->
<section class="py-24 px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop bg-surface">
<div class="max-w-max-width mx-auto">
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-on-surface mb-12 text-center">CV analizinin ötesinde.</h2>
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow flex flex-col items-start">
<div class="p-3 bg-surface rounded-lg mb-6">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container">troubleshoot</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-on-surface mb-2">Detaylı Analiz</h3>
<p class="font-body-sm text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">Sadece anahtar kelimeleri değil, deneyiminizin bağlamını ve derinliğini de değerlendiririz.</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow flex flex-col items-start">
<div class="p-3 bg-surface rounded-lg mb-6">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container">fitness_center</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-on-surface mb-2">Güçlü Yönler</h3>
<p class="font-body-sm text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">Sizi diğer adaylardan ayıran benzersiz becerilerinizi belirler ve vurgular.</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow flex flex-col items-start">
<div class="p-3 bg-surface rounded-lg mb-6">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container">trending_up</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-on-surface mb-2">Gelişim Alanları</h3>
<p class="font-body-sm text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">Kariyer hedeflerinize ulaşmanız için aşmanız gereken engelleri dürüstçe gösterir.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- 7. TESTIMONIALS -->
<section class="bg-surface-container-lowest py-24 px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
<div class="max-w-max-width mx-auto">
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-on-surface mb-12 text-center">Adaylar ne diyor?</h2>
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
<div class="bg-surface p-8 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant shadow-sm flex flex-col">
<div class="flex text-secondary mb-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings: &quot;FILL&quot; 1;">star</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings: &quot;FILL&quot; 1;">star</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings: &quot;FILL&quot; 1;">star</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings: &quot;FILL&quot; 1;">star</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings: &quot;FILL&quot; 1;">star</span>
</div>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-8 flex-grow">"Beacon sayesinde CV'mdeki ufak ama kritik hataları fark ettim. Düzeltmeleri yaptıktan sonra ilk hafta içinde 3 mülakat daveti aldım. Kesinlikle tavsiye ederim."</p>
<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary-container text-white flex items-center justify-center font-label-md text-label-md">AK</div>
<span class="font-headline-sm text-body-md font-semibold text-on-surface">Ayşe K.</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="bg-surface p-8 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant shadow-sm flex flex-col">
<div class="flex text-secondary mb-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings: &quot;FILL&quot; 1;">star</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings: &quot;FILL&quot; 1;">star</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings: &quot;FILL&quot; 1;">star</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings: &quot;FILL&quot; 1;">star</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings: &quot;FILL&quot; 1;">star</span>
</div>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-8 flex-grow">"Yazılım alanında iş arıyordum ama CV'm çok standarttı. Analiz raporu bana yeteneklerimi nasıl daha teknik bir dille ifade edebileceğimi gösterdi."</p>
<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary-container text-white flex items-center justify-center font-label-md text-label-md">MT</div>
<span class="font-headline-sm text-body-md font-semibold text-on-surface">Mert T.</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="bg-surface p-8 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant shadow-sm flex flex-col">
<div class="flex text-secondary mb-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings: &quot;FILL&quot; 1;">star</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings: &quot;FILL&quot; 1;">star</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings: &quot;FILL&quot; 1;">star</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings: &quot;FILL&quot; 1;">star</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">star_half</span>
</div>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-8 flex-grow">"Gelişim önerileri kısmı harika. Sadece 'bu eksik' demiyor, 'şunu öğrenmelisin' diyerek somut bir hedef koyuyor önünüze."</p>
<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary-container text-white flex items-center justify-center font-label-md text-label-md">SA</div>
<span class="font-headline-sm text-body-md font-semibold text-on-surface">Selin A.</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- 8. FAQ -->
<section class="py-24 px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop bg-surface">
<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-on-surface mb-12 text-center">Sık sorulan sorular.</h2>
<div class="space-y-4">
<details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-outline-variant shadow-sm [&amp;_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
<summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-on-surface">
<span class="">Beacon ücretsiz mi?</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container transition group-open:rotate-180">add</span>
</summary>
<div class="px-6 pb-6 font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
                        Evet, temel CV analiz hizmetimiz tamamen ücretsizdir.
                    </div>
</details>
<details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-outline-variant shadow-sm [&amp;_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
<summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-on-surface">
<span class="">Hangi formatlar destekleniyor?</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container transition group-open:rotate-180">add</span>
</summary>
<div class="px-6 pb-6 font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
                        Şu anda PDF ve DOCX (Microsoft Word) formatlarını destekliyoruz.
                    </div>
</details>
<details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-outline-variant shadow-sm [&amp;_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
<summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-on-surface">
<span class="">Analiz ne kadar sürer?</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container transition group-open:rotate-180">add</span>
</summary>
<div class="px-6 pb-6 font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
                        Analiz genellikle saniyeler içinde tamamlanır ve sonuçlar anında ekranda gösterilir.
                    </div>
</details>
<details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-outline-variant shadow-sm [&amp;_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
<summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-on-surface">
<span class="">Verilerim güvende mi?</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container transition group-open:rotate-180">add</span>
</summary>
<div class="px-6 pb-6 font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
